query:
SELECT 
  id,
  smshubActivationId,
  phoneNumber,
  apiId,
  status,
  smsCode,
  TIMESTAMPDIFF(SECOND, createdAt, NOW()) as seconds_ago
FROM activations
WHERE status IN ('active', 'pending')
ORDER BY id DESC
LIMIT 3;
